Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:11.63,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,Living your life is a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:16.00,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,But one step ahead,\NI hear there's only darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.14,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,Art is long. Life is short.
