Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:31.31,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't want\Nregrets in your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:34.66,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be your ultimate weapon.
