Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:01:00.78,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,It's romance for sure.\NWe're sexy men for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:04.65,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,If you dare to dream, it will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:07.55,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,After this great love of ours...
