Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting\Nfor you, Mr. Kanoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:58.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Axi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:08.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:19.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Te...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You look well...\NBetter than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:32.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You too. I haven't seen you since\Nthe day you came to borrow money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you planning\Nto bilk us from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:41.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let the boy\Noff the hook for now, Kanoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:46.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask you to come all this way\Nto discuss trivial matters like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:49.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which is more trivial?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:53.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A crooked casino that strips amateur\Ngamblers of all they've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:55.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mr. Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, how dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:03.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be upfront about this... I just want\Nto do some business with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In a peaceful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:11.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to hand\Noveryoung Ayase there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:16.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you'll be compensated.\NI'll pay you back your 120 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:21.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll add another 10 million\Nto the total. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning to resell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've found\Na higher bidder, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that's a surprising scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you\Nto misunderstand, Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:39.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's appeared who heard of\Nyour plight and decided to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's even offering to adopt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:46.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but he says\Nhe'll pay off my debt too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:49.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally be free again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll be rich.\NIsn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's settled, right, Yukiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:58.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:03.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to get a job\Nand pay the debt off yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:07.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I think your mindset\Nand life-style will both change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:12.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who has to change.\NOr you may end up in a vicious circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing, lecturing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're just Yukiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:20.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it that way,\NTetsuo. I'll help you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:24.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just do\Nwhat I say, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:27.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishii is absolutely right. Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:30.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...reality isn't so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:33.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you for your\Nown good. Do as I suggested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:37.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The patron has status and honor.\NQuite the gentleman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Outwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:45.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He also has sexual propensities\Nthat can't be made public, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:50.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As a sadist, he'll train\Nyou till you're insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:54.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll be eaten alive\Nby hedonistic sexual gourmands...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:59.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this is a place where a corrupt\Ncrowd comes to buy their next prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:02.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hardly expect them\Nto treat you like a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:06.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that and\Nstill want to sell him off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, lshii?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:14.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you save yourself,\Nyou don't care what happens to Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:22.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, it's too late.\NI won the bid for Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's invalid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:28.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That auction was restricted\Nto mem bers, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake\Nto hand over the product...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:35.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...to someone who entered\Nthe premises under false pretenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, take our money\Nlike a good boy and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:46.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was participating\Non behalf of a certain member.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:50.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've paid you and taken\Npossession, this kid belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:59.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?\NWhy don't we make a wager?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:05.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, I'll contact my client\Nto tell him that the deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:10.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, I'll return your 120\Nmillion, along with an extra 50 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:14.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does that mean\Nyou'll get Ayase for free...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:18.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll also earn a cool\N50 million without lifting a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you lose, you'll have\Nto give that kid back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:25.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I won't repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:32.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, I want you to add another\N200 million as an "inconvenience fee."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:37.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I want you to transfer\Nall of Tetsuo lshii's debt to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:41.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me? W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can accept these\Nnew terms, I'll take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:51.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's nothing I can do\Nto rip lshii out of Ayase's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:54.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have no choice\Nbut to keep him close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me add another condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:05.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll close your loan shark\Nbusiness and leave Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:08.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll also apologize for insulting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:12.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you don't think you\Ncan make it out of here alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:16.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal's done.\NLet's get this show on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:22.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 320 million yen here,\Nand these are all of lshii's debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:27.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:28.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks fine.\NThen come overto this table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come over to this table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:35.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've closed the place tonight\Nfor you, but we're both busy men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:38.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A speedy conclusion is best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The trigger can't be pulled\Nif the cylinder can't rotate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:53.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him go, Kuba.\NThat was just a demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:09.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We load the gun with one bullet,\Nthen take turns pulling the trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...and whoever's out of luck loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:17.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That said, it's just\Nloaded with red ink, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:21.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had these guns and bullets\Nmade just for this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:26.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's a real gun that can fire\Nlive bullets like the ones from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hand him the gun.\NAnd a new bullet too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:34.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want you\Nto suspect me of conning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel safer\Nloading it yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:45.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You accepted my terms\Nbecause you're sure you'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be a con.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:54.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like people could play fair here.\NServes you right, Kanoh, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:59.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get shut down and driven out.\NI just can't wait to see him eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:10.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask something, Kanoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:13.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so\Nhung up on this kid's welfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:19.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be far safer and beneficial for you\Nto take the money and hand him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:24.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What possible reason could\Nyou have for taking such a risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:43.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you don't seem\Nto remember anything about it, Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time around...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm going to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:02.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he talking about? Don't tell\Nme you knew him from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:07.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be out of your\Nmind from all the tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have one bullet left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be settled in the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:16.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:31.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all over in\Nthis round! Your life, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them alone!\NHe's about to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:42.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make you feel good?\NHe put you through hell too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:46.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:50.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so good to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:01.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh! You mustn't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:04.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! This gun is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:05.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...said it for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,My name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:36.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what are you doing, Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time...\NMr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:52.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:58.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sit back and watch.\NI'm an extremely lucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:03.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like I can lose today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:15.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Lucky, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:40.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!\NThere's no way that could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanoh, how the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:49.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like\Nit was a done deal that I'd lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mr. Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:58.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry things didn't go as you planned.\NKuba, take this money to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:12:59.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you too,\Nlshii. Don't run off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:05.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:09.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You pretended to load it at the start,\Nbut you didn't put any bullets in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:14.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying such a petty trick...\NDon't think you're leaving here alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:17.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:25.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.\NThe chamber's empty after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:34.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,True, I didn't load this paint bullet, but\NI did load something else in its place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:37.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Four, five...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One bullet is missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me it's a live bullet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:52.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As a reward for giving the correct\Nanswer, I'll take you for a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, out of my way! Step aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:14:00.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now... If it makes you\Nthat happy, it makes me happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:03.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it'll be a fun trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:11.17,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It finally went down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:15.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You nearly gave me a heart attack.\NCollapsing as soon as we got home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:20.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,About lshii...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:31.25,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering what that bastard did,\Nselling his organs won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:39.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once,\NI'll forgive him for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:42.57,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll make\Nsure he pays me back in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing wholesome manual labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.40,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:03.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, being family is on a different\Nlevel, with no bearing on like or dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it still pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:11.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,To see the person I love look so\Ndamn happy over another man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't it be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:21.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't I ever be your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:24.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lived here together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:29.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you and I are total strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:34.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But even your parents\Nstarted out as strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:40.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you can become family\Neven when not tied by blood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Wait, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right.\NThere's something I wanted to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:10.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We've met before\Nsomewhere, you and l, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:16.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me.\NI can't remember, and l...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:27.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point unless you\Nrecall these things on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:35.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. But on the other hand,\Nif you do, I'll make this go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:44.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I make lshii pay\Nback what he owes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:48.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll still be in the red for\Nthe amount I bid on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the repayment during\Nyesterday's showdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's money I earned\Nputting my life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do\Nwith your debt to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\NI'm charging 10/10 interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:01.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,10/10?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:05.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means\N10% interest every 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:08.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You start accruing interest\Nthe day your loan begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:12.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...so if you borrow\Nthe whole 120 million from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:16.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...that means you're really\N132 million in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:20.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In 10 days, the interest is 13 million.\NIt's 14.6 million after 20 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:25.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In otherwords, after 30 days, you'll\Nowe me 57.2 million just in interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd include interest when I close\Nthe books every 10 days...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:33.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...but in your case,\NI think I'll give you a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:37.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Be happy. I rounded off the total.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand, Ayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't do it. All that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:02.33,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you have it.\NAn amazing potential to earn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:08.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you before, I'll pay you\N500,000 yen each time we have sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:12.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Let go of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:16.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job.\NYou even came so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You said we were\Ngoing to be family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:26.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even family members need to be\Nscrupulous about money matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should let you know that\N"500,000 yen a time"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...means each time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:41.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I confessed my love,\Nhad sex, and started living with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:44.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...doesn't mean I can ever rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, Mr. Ayase is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because in my case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:59.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(598,248)}Sex\N(Rape)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:59.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(452,293)}Living\NTogether\N(lncarceration)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:59.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(361,271)}Confessed\NLove
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:59.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(307,343)}(I think\NI did)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:59.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything way, way out of order
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting, Ayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:11.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, anything's fine with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't do. He's about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:25.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! Kanoh, when are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:35.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... You certainly went for\Na type you don't usually go for...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I admit he's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:45.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! How rude of me\Nnot to even introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoruko Someya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to work at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you sick tranny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:01.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NCan't you just lend him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:03.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lending him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:07.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll seriously kick you off\Na high-rise, you queer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're a homo yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:12.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:16.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But then why'd you\Ndo all those things to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:27.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What an intriguing young man...\NI really must get my hands on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:32.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanoh here is a homo all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:36.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the kind of man who never\Nrecognized the rights of transvestites.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:39.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But here he is with\Na crush on a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:43.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really have an obligation\Nto worship that young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:47.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up! I'm still not a homo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:50.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what are "all those things"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's special...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:53.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:55.67,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A call from Mr. Takanohashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:59.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better get out, pervert.\NYou're scaring Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.41,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:05.85,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I've got to go.\NIt was lovely chatting with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:08.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,For me too. I enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:12.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Someya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:19.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I get him to warm\Nup to me? He's so friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:29.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true he seems very quiet, so you\Nneed to break the ice somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:32.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I wouldn't\Nbe having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your punishment for breaking\Nso many women's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:40.55,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Faced with one immune to your looks,\Nbody, and money... Serves you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:45.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, if you took away those three\Nthings, I wonder what would be left...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:49.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! I'll send\Nsomething useful over later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What? Hand it over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret. Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:54.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:00.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's useful about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:02.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard... Messing with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,How to Tame Small Animals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:09.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm not the only one who sees\NAyase as a small creature like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's got brown hair,\Nis small, and has big eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:16.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Smart Way\Nto Tame Your Pet, Day One.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:20.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stressful for an animal\Nto be in a new environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:23.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch them or go near them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:28.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,As they're very small and delicate,\Nnever treat them with violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:33.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(416,281)}Day\NOne: \NRape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:33.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:34.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this thing! How can this help?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:38.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:42.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(608,271)}Never\Ntreat\Nthem\Nwith\Nviolence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:45.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There was a roach...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.06,0:22:50.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Such clean\Napartments still have cockroaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:51.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This book...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:54.62,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's from Someya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.73,0:22:57.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some kind of pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:03.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say it's to help\Nme get close to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:06.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... may I read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:07.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:10.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:15.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... He's so sweet looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:19.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to touch him...\Nkiss him... make love to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:20.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:25.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(558,370)}Don't\Ntouch\Nthem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:25.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(474,372)}or\Ngo\Nnear\Nthem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:25.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(343,310)}on\Nthe\Nfirst\Nday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:30.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the office.\NYou go on to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:33.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go to bed, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:36.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be with him and not have sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:44.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Day two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:48.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pet still hasn't gotten\Nused to his new environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:50.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.62,0:23:51.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:56.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call him by his name in a gentle voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:01.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be late again tonight,\Nso eat without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.73,0:24:03.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:08.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:12.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home. You're early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:16.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just came for a change\Nof clothes. I'll be heading right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:17.84,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.92,0:24:19.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:21.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase...\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.72,0:24:26.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,After a few days,\Nyou'll be allowed to touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.26,0:24:29.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stroke him gently on\Nthe head and develop affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.89,0:24:30.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.46,0:24:32.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.23,0:24:38.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important at this time\Nnot to pursue him too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.07,0:24:41.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I touch him, I'll lose all reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.81,0:24:45.48,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The trick is to not ever scare him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.48,0:24:47.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to like\Nsake more than you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.65,0:24:57.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do mice and rabbits\Ndrink sake nowadays?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.16,0:25:00.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of nonsense is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.26,0:25:03.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And a few days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:06.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.\NAre you going to work again tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.53,0:25:07.69,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.13,0:25:12.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you work hard at it,\Nyour efforts will be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.40,0:25:16.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished up at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.11,0:25:19.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll start to display trust\Nand affection towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.68,0:25:23.11,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,True, my efforts have been rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.21,0:25:28.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But at a cost. The celibate life\NI've been leading for the last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.22,0:25:31.59,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning if this goes on, I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.69,0:25:34.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...get to have a physical\Nrelationship with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.63,0:25:37.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, there'd be no point!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.50,0:25:41.09,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could fix you something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.20,0:25:45.16,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea. I'd like something\Nlight to go with my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.27,0:25:46.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.70,0:25:51.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, then just for a little while.\NI'll start making it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:55.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to become\Na good-natured owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.58,0:25:58.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it tonight for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.82,0:26:03.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is make\Nsure I don't scare him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.89,0:26:12.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.40,0:26:15.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can drink some more...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.93,0:26:18.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't fall asleep on me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.76,0:26:48.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.20,0:26:50.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.37,0:26:51.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.00,0:26:56.77,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe he normally\Nflinches from my touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.61,0:27:00.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.71,0:27:03.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.78,0:27:07.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He still thinks of me as a kind\Nowner, even when it comes to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.85,0:27:12.38,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was starting to think that\Nyou were avoiding me, Mr. Kanoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.29,0:27:17.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We never eat together,\Nand you always run off somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.33,0:27:18.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.36,0:27:20.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.60,0:27:24.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the other day\Nwhen you said I was special?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.27,0:27:27.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.37,0:27:29.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That day?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.97,0:27:31.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's special!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.58,0:27:35.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried, but since\Nyou said that about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.41,0:27:38.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.92,0:27:41.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.65,0:27:47.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Words I unknowingly said worked\Nbetterthan my efforts these few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.13,0:27:49.56,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're special.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.96,0:27:52.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.23,0:27:55.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... You're special, very special.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.47,0:27:59.13,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're special.\NIn more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.44,0:28:02.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.61,0:28:04.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.18,0:28:08.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I think I've seen the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.01,0:28:10.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.85,0:28:14.44,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with elaborate\Ntricks and forced restraint.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.55,0:28:18.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it's better to be\Nstraightforward when expressing love.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.16,0:28:31.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You threw that book away?\NSo cruel! I was trying to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.40,0:28:35.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that. You were\Nhaving fun messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.91,0:28:38.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again,\Ntaking it the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.04,0:28:41.74,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that you were totally off the mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.85,0:28:43.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm going with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.65,0:28:47.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did read it? You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.55,0:28:51.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what kind of man you are...\NCould this also be because of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.72,0:28:53.71,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not to be sold short.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.82,0:28:55.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where's Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:28:58.29,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.33,0:29:03.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a hangover.\NWhen should I have him drink next?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.43,0:29:07.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Going with the flow" is different\Nfrom "succumbing to instinct."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.57,0:29:13.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going\Nto drink alcohol again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.41,0:29:22.88,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,When I opened\Nthe window and spoke to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.99,0:29:29.05,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I could see that the wintry\Nnight sky was sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.46,0:29:35.13,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the emotions\Nof all the people everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.23,0:29:41.33,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...had turned into those stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.91,0:29:49.04,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,That promise we made so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.15,0:29:54.28,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...is something I still\Ncling tightly to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.38,0:30:03.62,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,On sleepless nights in my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.66,0:30:12.76,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if a single tear falls...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.87,0:30:18.97,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never forget that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.08,0:30:30.75,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved,\Njust keep me warm forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.39,0:30:37.02,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm caught in a rainfall of grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.13,0:30:44.00,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want to become your love.
